{"id":"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions","title":"InMemoryScrollingOptions","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions\", \"name\": \"InMemoryScrollingOptions\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/router_config.ts#L125-L177\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"inmemoryscrollingoptions\">InMemoryScrollingOptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#inmemoryscrollingoptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2185em3ssff1exwg04gon8psy\">可與 <code><a href=\"api/router/withInMemoryScrolling\" class=\"code-anchor\">withInMemoryScrolling</a></code> 函式一起使用的捲動屬性的設定選項。</p>\n\n  </section><section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">InMemoryScrollingOptions</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#anchorScrolling\"><span class=\"member-name\">anchorScrolling</span>?: 'disabled' | 'enabled'</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#scrollPositionRestoration\"><span class=\"member-name\">scrollPositionRestoration</span>?: 'disabled' | 'enabled' | 'top'</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  <div class=\"descendants interface\">\n    <h2 id=\"子介面\">子介面<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#子介面\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <code><a href=\"api/router/ExtraOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">ExtraOptions</a></code>\n    \n  </li>\n</ul>\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"anchorScrolling\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">anchorScrolling</span>?: 'disabled' | 'enabled'</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3iycgdka329qvzy2n87wr9ned\">設定為 『enabled』 時，如果 URL 有一個片段，就捲動到錨點元素。預設情況下，錨定捲動是停用的。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"25klvzuefrk045w0d4syorrcl\">錨點捲動不會在 『popstate』 上發生。相反，我們會恢復儲存的位置或捲動到頂部。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"scrollPositionRestoration\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">scrollPositionRestoration</span>?: 'disabled' | 'enabled' | 'top'</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"43gk3wgynamjc67yoyatvrlmx\">設定是否需要在導向回來的時候恢復捲動位置。</p>\n          <ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b4rnssawhbhjdtvlmlkki5b8z\">'disabled' - 什麼也不做（預設）。在導向時，會自動維護捲動位置。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d50llwu19ns9i4v88xmmnnsk\">'top' - 在任何一次導向中都把捲動位置設定為 x=0, y=0。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"tuh6jjq2xbesqln7jf3bxzf0\">  'enabled' —— 當向後導向時，捲動到以前的捲動位置。當向前導向時，如果提供了錨點，則自動捲動到那個錨點，否則把捲動位置設定為 [0, 0]。該選項將來會變成預設值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9u8k17y030c7usclpwztx9xhe\">你可以像下面的例子一樣適配它啟用時的行為，來自定義恢復捲動位置的策略：。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nclass AppComponent {\n  movieData: any;\n\n  constructor(private router: <a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a>, private viewportScroller: <a href=\"api/common/ViewportScroller\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewportScroller</a>,\nchangeDetectorRef: <a href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ChangeDetectorRef</a>) {\n  router.events.pipe(filter((event: <a href=\"api/router/Event\" class=\"code-anchor\">Event</a>): event is <a href=\"api/router/Scroll\" class=\"code-anchor\">Scroll</a> =&gt; event instanceof <a href=\"api/router/Scroll\" class=\"code-anchor\">Scroll</a>)\n    ).subscribe(e =&gt; {\n      fetch('http://example.com/movies.json').then(response =&gt; {\n        this.movieData = response.json();\n        // update the template with the data before restoring scroll\n        changeDetectorRef.detectChanges();\n\n        if (e.position) {\n          viewportScroller.scrollToPosition(e.position);\n        }\n      });\n    });\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router\n - api/router/ExtraOptions\n - api/router/withInMemoryScrolling\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/ViewportScroller\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\n - api/router\n - api/router/Event\n - api/router/ExtraOptions\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#anchorScrolling\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#inmemoryscrollingoptions\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#instance-properties\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#scrollPositionRestoration\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingOptions#子介面\n - api/router/Router\n - api/router/Scroll\n - api/router/withInMemoryScrolling\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/router_config.ts#L125-L177\n-->"}